title: [Western Waterway, Charl's Teeth]
description: Beautiful blue waters stretch far to the west before crashing against peaks of dark volcanic material.  Smaller boulders dot the ocean floor, having fallen from the larger spires.  Wind and erosion have taken their toll on the surface, creating tunnels and shapes in the hard rock.
